---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research Consultancy | Doctoral College UK" description="DCUK's research consultancy services — applied organisational research, evidence reviews, and methodology support for public, private, and third sector organisations.">

  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Research Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Research Consultancy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">DCUK offers applied research consultancy to organisations seeking rigorous, evidence-based answers to management and organisational challenges. We bring academic expertise and practitioner insight to the questions that matter most to your organisation.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we offer -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Services</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Applied Organisational Research</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">We design and conduct primary research within your organisation — using interviews, surveys, observation, and document analysis — to investigate specific management challenges. Our approach is rigorous, ethical, and produces findings that are both trustworthy and practically actionable.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Suitable for: understanding why a change initiative is not working, investigating the causes of staff turnover, examining leadership effectiveness, or exploring the factors shaping a specific organisational challenge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Evidence Reviews</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">We conduct systematic or rapid reviews of the academic and grey literature on a specific management topic, synthesising what is known, identifying what the evidence supports, and translating findings into practical implications for your organisation or sector.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Suitable for: informing a strategic decision, building the evidence base for a new initiative, reviewing the effectiveness of an intervention type, or understanding international best practice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Programme Evaluation</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">We design and conduct independent evaluations of leadership development programmes, organisational change initiatives, and workforce development interventions. Our evaluations combine quantitative outcome measurement with qualitative process investigation.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Suitable for: assessing the impact of a training investment, building an evidence base for scaling an initiative, or meeting funder or board requirements for independent evaluation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Research Methodology Support</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">We provide expert support for organisations developing their own research or evaluation capacity — including research design, questionnaire and interview guide development, qualitative analysis, and statistical support.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Suitable for: HR or OD teams conducting internal people research, organisations building evaluation capability, or teams needing analytical support for specific projects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Bespoke Research Training</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">We deliver bespoke research methods training for professional teams — covering qualitative research, survey design, interview skills, and evidence literacy for managers. Delivered online or in-person, half-day to two-day formats.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Suitable for: HR, OD, and strategy teams; healthcare professionals undertaking service evaluation; educators implementing evidence-informed practice; or any professional group needing applied research skills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Keynote and Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">DCUK faculty are available for keynote presentations at organisational events, conferences, and leadership development days — covering management research, doctoral education, and leadership in practice.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Contact us with your requirements and we will provide a proposal tailored to your event or advisory needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Process</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">01</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Initial Conversation</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">A free 30-minute call to understand your challenge, discuss what research could offer, and determine whether DCUK is the right partner.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">02</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Proposal</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">We provide a written proposal setting out the research question, methodology, timeline, deliverables, and fee. All proposals are fixed-fee.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">03</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Research</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">We conduct the research according to the agreed methodology, maintaining regular communication with your team and providing interim updates as agreed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-3">04</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Findings and Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">We deliver a written report and a presentation of findings, and remain available for follow-up conversations to support the application of findings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Start the conversation</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">All consultancy enquiries begin with a free, no-obligation conversation. Email us with a brief description of your challenge and we will arrange a call.</p>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">Email: <a href="mailto:research@doctoralcollege.ac.uk" class="text-accent hover:underline">research@doctoralcollege.ac.uk</a> with the subject line "Consultancy Enquiry".</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="mailto:research@doctoralcollege.ac.uk?subject=Consultancy%20Enquiry" class="btn-primary">Email us now</a>
        <a href="/connect" class="btn-outline">Other ways to connect</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
